{{Infobox bus accident |title = 2015 Brazil bus accident |image = Santa Catarina in Brazil.svg |caption = Location of Santa Catarina in Brazil |date = 15 March 2015 |location = Santa Catarina |country = Brazil |line = |operator = |owner = |type = |cause = |buses = |other = |pax = |peds = |deaths = 54 <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/reuters/article-2995365/Up-51-dead-bus-crash-southern-Brazil.html|title=Up to 51 dead after bus crash in southern Brazil|work=Mail Online}}</ref><ref>https://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2015/03/15/world/americas/ap-lt-brazil-bus-accident.html</ref> |injuries = 7 |damage = |property = }}
The '''2015 Brazil bus accident''' occurred on 15 March 2015, when a tourist bus left the road and plunged approximately {{convert|100|m|ft}} near the city of [[Joinville]] in [[Santa Catarina (state)|Santa Catarina]] state, [[Brazil]]. At least 51 people died and 7 were injured in the accident.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2015/03/15/us-brazil-crash-idUSKBN0MB02Y20150315|title=Up to 51 dead after bus crash in southern Brazil|work=Reuters}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Bus plunge in southern Brazil leaves 49 dead|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-latin-america-31899506|publisher=BBC|accessdate=15 March 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2015/03/15/us-brazil-crash-idUSKBN0MB0SJ20150315|title=Bus plunges off cliff in Brazil, 54 killed|work=Reuters}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.yahoo.com/bus-crash-kills-30-brazil-001702773.html;_ylt=AwrSyCXk0QRVpW8AwLHQtDMD|title=54 dead in Brazil bus crash: Rousseff|date=15 March 2015|work=Yahoo News}}</ref>
==Incident== The bus veered off the road and plunged into a ravine in the southern Brazilian province of Santa Carina.<ref>http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2015-03/15/c_134068577.htm</ref>
